    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 3'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='900' maxwidth='1500' minheight='900' minwidth='1500' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='55000' id='3' name='Satisfaction level by Tenure' w='98933' x='333' y='222' />
        <zone h='44333' id='5' name='Tenure Histogram' w='41333' x='333' y='54556' />
        <zone h='7444' id='6' name='Tenure Histogram' pane-specification-id='1' param='[federated.09onw4n18ceu1b1dz2kx20464naf].[none:left:ok]' type-v2='color' w='3933' x='96067' y='6778' />
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='35222' id='7' type-v2='text' w='54000' x='44533' y='61222'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#e15759' fontsize='10'>INSIGHTS</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'>1. Employees who left fall into two general categories: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>dissatisfied employees with shorter tenures</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'> and </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>very satisfied employees with medium-length tenures.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'>2. </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>Four-year employees who left seem to have an unusually low satisfaction level.</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'>Æ </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'>It&apos;s worth investigating changes to company policy</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'> that might have affected people specifically at the four-year mark, if possible. </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'>3. The longest-tenured employees didn&apos;t leave. Their satisfaction levels aligned with those of newer employees who stayed. </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'>4. The histogram shows that there are</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'> relatively few longer-tenured employees</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000'>. It&apos;s possible that</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000'> they&apos;re the higher-ranking, higher-paid employees.</run>
          </formatted-text>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
